node.text: I’m so excited to partner with @varsitytutors to teach a couple interactive classes! Come draw with me! Join me and @VarsityTutors on July 19th for my free, live draw-along as we explore the art of drawing human faces and making them come alive. You’ll leave class with an animated character of your own, plus collaborate with me to create the ultimate character to define “summer.” Bring your pens, pencils, curiosity and creativity. Sign up today! Link in bio!  #VarsityTutors #AD

node.text:
Guys my art is in a coloring book!!! 🤩 I’m so excited!!! @tiktok has teamed up with some of the top illustrators to bring some of the most recognizable trends from the TikTok universe to life in a Coloring Book & Art Set which will be EXCLUSIVELY available on the #NTWRK app.
Featuring designs by @leversandpulleys, @creative_carrah, @mikebennettart, me, @frankynines & @coolman_coffeedan, "A TikTok Coloring Book" is a collection of original artwork created to inspire fans to create their own masterpiece. Tune in on March 16th at 7PM ET / 4PM PT to secure your very own.
